videos.description: John Mooney gets the nice pass from Rex Pflueger and goes up strong through the contact to throw down a dunk and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Mooney finishes strong with and-1 dunk

videos.description: Jalen Hill comes up with a massive block on the defensive end, and Kris Wilkes comes up clutch hitting a 3-pointer in transition for the win and falls over in a heap due to a leg cramp afterward.
videos.headline: Wilkes sinks game-winner from deep
